1
00:00:39,020 --> 00:00:40,360
May I be like the stars

2
00:00:40,380 --> 00:00:41,580
and you like the moon.

3
00:00:42,450 --> 00:00:43,670
As long as the world remains,

4
00:00:44,780 --> 00:00:45,780
so shall we.

5
00:01:01,720 --> 00:01:03,830
I only wish to stay with the one I love,

6
00:01:04,430 --> 00:01:06,060
watching every sunrise and sunset.

7
00:01:07,640 --> 00:01:09,370
I want to be with you forever.

8
00:01:13,620 --> 00:01:14,920
Eternals and demons walk different paths.

9
00:01:15,640 --> 00:01:17,480
You and she are ultimately different.

10
00:01:37,970 --> 00:01:39,600
Have you ever

11
00:01:40,220 --> 00:01:41,789
truly cared for me?

12
00:01:44,440 --> 00:01:45,250
No.

13
00:01:45,660 --> 00:01:46,360
Never.

14
00:01:54,650 --> 00:01:57,720
In this life and the next, through all lifetimes…

15
00:02:02,150 --> 00:02:03,310
May we live and die together,

16
00:02:04,400 --> 00:02:06,040
and share life and death as one.

17
00:02:41,710 --> 00:02:45,790
[Moonlight Mystique]

18
00:02:46,410 --> 00:02:50,000
[Episode 40]

19
00:02:50,560 --> 00:02:51,840
I just want to complete

20
00:02:51,840 --> 00:02:53,950
what was left unfinished 60,000 years ago.

21
00:02:53,980 --> 00:02:55,980
So, whether you are Xing Yue or not,

22
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:57,410
just for that face of yours,

23
00:02:57,440 --> 00:02:59,040
I must marry you.

24
00:03:00,940 --> 00:03:02,300
You have no choice.

25
00:03:03,250 --> 00:03:05,000
Before I say yes,

26
00:03:05,020 --> 00:03:06,570
I want a promise from you.

27
00:03:06,640 --> 00:03:07,590
Go ahead.

28
00:03:08,270 --> 00:03:11,070
You must never harm any living being in this world again.

29
00:03:11,090 --> 00:03:13,850
Since killing them is so easy for you,

30
00:03:13,880 --> 00:03:15,890
why bother with such boring acts?

31
00:03:19,680 --> 00:03:21,579
If you're negotiating with me as the wife

32
00:03:21,600 --> 00:03:22,880
of the Hidden Lord,

33
00:03:23,850 --> 00:03:25,079
I will comply with your terms.

34
00:03:25,100 --> 00:03:25,820
Alright.

35
00:03:26,570 --> 00:03:27,450
I promise you.

36
00:03:32,829 --> 00:03:34,140
Tomorrow,

37
00:03:34,780 --> 00:03:35,900
the Lunar Hidden Sea

38
00:03:36,520 --> 00:03:38,290
will be our wedding venue.

39
00:03:39,780 --> 00:03:41,680
The Lunar Hidden Sea has long disappeared.

40
00:03:42,360 --> 00:03:43,940
60,000 years ago,

41
00:03:44,290 --> 00:03:45,940
Jing Yuan could replicate Xing Yue Pavilion

42
00:03:46,000 --> 00:03:48,360
for Xing Yue in the Demon Race's territory.

43
00:03:48,720 --> 00:03:50,400
Likewise, here in the Eastern Continent,

44
00:03:50,420 --> 00:03:51,910
I can replicate the Lunar Hidden Sea for you.

45
00:03:53,060 --> 00:03:55,180
I want everything

46
00:03:55,210 --> 00:03:57,490
to be exactly as it was 60,000 years ago.

47
00:04:17,420 --> 00:04:18,390
Master,

48
00:04:19,050 --> 00:04:20,579
Bai Shuo was right.

49
00:04:21,459 --> 00:04:23,780
Everyone has their own responsibilities to fulfil.

50
00:04:25,040 --> 00:04:27,070
For the future of the Fox Clan,

51
00:04:27,460 --> 00:04:28,790
Mu Jiu sacrificed himself;

52
00:04:29,340 --> 00:04:32,170
To settle old grudges,

53
00:04:32,190 --> 00:04:33,590
Cang Shan gave his life;

54
00:04:34,490 --> 00:04:36,659
To protect the Polar Region,

55
00:04:37,140 --> 00:04:38,530
you hurt yourself.

56
00:04:40,080 --> 00:04:41,880
To protect the world, Bai Shuo bravely went

57
00:04:42,880 --> 00:04:44,480
to face the danger.

58
00:04:45,900 --> 00:04:47,010
And I...

59
00:04:48,190 --> 00:04:50,240
have my own things to do.

60
00:06:05,950 --> 00:06:07,510
This wedding gown

61
00:06:08,500 --> 00:06:10,800
is exactly the same as the one from 60,000 years ago.

62
00:06:12,400 --> 00:06:13,540
Try it on.

63
00:06:19,850 --> 00:06:21,360
You'll wear it eventually.

64
00:06:21,950 --> 00:06:24,680
Whether it's marrying you or taking control of the world,

65
00:06:24,700 --> 00:06:27,210
I will reclaim everything I've lost.

66
00:06:28,620 --> 00:06:29,940
Stop it.

67
00:06:30,230 --> 00:06:31,870
What's the meaning of all this?

68
00:06:32,570 --> 00:06:33,520
The meaning?

69
00:06:33,740 --> 00:06:36,130
I'm the meaning of this world, aren't I?

70
00:06:36,150 --> 00:06:37,840
If you keep being so arrogant,

71
00:06:37,870 --> 00:06:40,820
you will never understand the true love and sincerity of this world.

72
00:06:40,840 --> 00:06:43,050
Even if you possess 10,000 years of divine power,

73
00:06:43,080 --> 00:06:44,590
it's all just emptiness.

74
00:06:44,870 --> 00:06:45,750
Only the weak

75
00:06:45,750 --> 00:06:48,159
chase after those meaningless meanings.

76
00:06:48,330 --> 00:06:50,570
My Divine Mirror reflects all things.

77
00:06:50,600 --> 00:06:53,070
It can also see all the evil thoughts in the world.

78
00:06:53,090 --> 00:06:54,580
Whether it's Eternals,

79
00:06:54,610 --> 00:06:57,050
demons, humans, or the Outlanders,

80
00:06:57,070 --> 00:06:58,090
all beings

81
00:06:58,130 --> 00:07:00,020
have their selfish and ugly sides.

82
00:07:00,050 --> 00:07:01,190
It was like this 60,000 years ago,

83
00:07:01,220 --> 00:07:02,560
and it will be the same 60,000 years later.

84
00:07:02,580 --> 00:07:03,900
Time will not make it

85
00:07:03,930 --> 00:07:05,240
any better.

86
00:07:05,260 --> 00:07:07,070
Is this the meaning you want?

87
00:07:07,810 --> 00:07:09,730
In this world, both good and evil exist.

88
00:07:10,410 --> 00:07:12,060
Good has meaning

89
00:07:12,710 --> 00:07:14,390
only in the face of evil.

90
00:07:15,650 --> 00:07:17,640
I won't waste words with you.

91
00:07:18,080 --> 00:07:19,490
After tomorrow's wedding,

92
00:07:19,510 --> 00:07:21,730
you will be my Divine Queen.

93
00:07:22,030 --> 00:07:23,910
All the good and evil in this world

94
00:07:23,930 --> 00:07:25,970
will no longer have anything to do with you.

95
00:07:34,110 --> 00:07:36,220
Don't struggle in vain.

96
00:07:37,060 --> 00:07:38,800
You have lost all your five Contemplations and divine power,

97
00:07:38,800 --> 00:07:39,980
leaving you weak.

98
00:07:40,240 --> 00:07:42,000
You can't stir up any more trouble.

99
00:08:51,440 --> 00:08:52,770
Tian Huo?

100
00:08:53,910 --> 00:08:55,380
Master, you're awake.

101
00:08:55,410 --> 00:08:56,220
Where is Bai Shuo?

102
00:08:58,550 --> 00:09:00,200
Xing Yue Divine Arrow has been repaired.

103
00:09:13,190 --> 00:09:14,610
How?

104
00:09:14,690 --> 00:09:15,690
This time,

105
00:09:16,140 --> 00:09:18,050
I didn't report to you in advance.

106
00:09:19,380 --> 00:09:21,400
Will you blame me?

107
00:09:31,340 --> 00:09:32,410
Tian Huo!

108
00:09:37,990 --> 00:09:38,820
Tian Huo,

109
00:09:38,850 --> 00:09:39,920
what's wrong with you?

110
00:09:46,060 --> 00:09:47,940
Why do you have no spiritual power at all?

111
00:09:48,660 --> 00:09:49,750
back then,

112
00:09:50,530 --> 00:09:52,290
when the first King of Outlanders

113
00:09:53,370 --> 00:09:55,960
saw the remnants of the Divine Arrow,

114
00:09:57,030 --> 00:09:59,810
he forged the Outlander King's Sword with his own blood.

115
00:10:00,510 --> 00:10:01,720
For a thousand years,

116
00:10:02,330 --> 00:10:04,400
only the Hua bloodline

117
00:10:04,580 --> 00:10:06,750
could pull out the Outlander King's Sword

118
00:10:06,780 --> 00:10:08,270
and infuse it with life.

119
00:10:08,290 --> 00:10:09,960
Now that the Outlander King's Sword is broken,

120
00:10:09,990 --> 00:10:11,230
I think

121
00:10:11,970 --> 00:10:15,230
only the spiritual blood of the Hua bloodline

122
00:10:16,030 --> 00:10:18,240
can restore the broken sword.

123
00:10:22,370 --> 00:10:23,260
It's okay.

124
00:10:23,740 --> 00:10:25,160
I... I'll save you.

125
00:10:27,930 --> 00:10:28,990
Master,

126
00:10:29,170 --> 00:10:30,710
don't waste your power.

127
00:10:31,210 --> 00:10:33,280
This is my own choice.

128
00:10:33,300 --> 00:10:34,510
I can save you.

129
00:10:34,540 --> 00:10:35,620
Master,

130
00:10:35,640 --> 00:10:36,640
it won't work.

131
00:10:36,670 --> 00:10:37,970
It'll work! I can save you!

132
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:38,890
Master.

133
00:10:39,800 --> 00:10:42,410
I also have my own mission.

134
00:10:43,110 --> 00:10:44,920
As the Outlanders' princess,

135
00:10:45,860 --> 00:10:47,920
I've been enjoying respect and honor since I was young,

136
00:10:50,140 --> 00:10:51,890
but not once have I

137
00:10:53,850 --> 00:10:56,380
shouldered the responsibilities that come with it.

138
00:10:57,140 --> 00:10:58,480
This time,

139
00:10:58,780 --> 00:11:00,690
I finally...

140
00:11:00,720 --> 00:11:04,740
I finally did the right thing.

141
00:11:11,340 --> 00:11:12,580
Bai Shuo...

142
00:11:12,790 --> 00:11:14,620
She went to the Cold Spring Palace.

143
00:11:14,910 --> 00:11:16,750
She didn't want me to tell you,

144
00:11:16,780 --> 00:11:18,240
but I know that

145
00:11:18,270 --> 00:11:21,450
if something were to happen to her,

146
00:11:22,840 --> 00:11:24,960
it would be a regret

147
00:11:25,620 --> 00:11:27,560
you would carry forever.

148
00:11:28,210 --> 00:11:29,300
Master,

149
00:11:29,730 --> 00:11:30,960
this journey

150
00:11:32,810 --> 00:11:34,670
has been so difficult.

151
00:11:35,280 --> 00:11:37,170
So many have already left us.

152
00:11:37,920 --> 00:11:40,650
Take the Divine Arrow and save her now.

153
00:11:41,710 --> 00:11:44,040
Don't leave any regrets.

154
00:11:54,850 --> 00:11:56,500
I'll leave these two

155
00:11:57,720 --> 00:12:00,260
to you for safekeeping.

156
00:12:06,050 --> 00:12:07,370
Don't be sad.

157
00:12:09,100 --> 00:12:10,280
I am just...

158
00:12:11,740 --> 00:12:13,850
going to find them.

159
00:12:16,620 --> 00:12:17,960
In this life,

160
00:12:20,220 --> 00:12:23,260
being able to follow you...

161
00:12:25,110 --> 00:12:26,420
leaves me...

162
00:12:28,490 --> 00:12:29,780
with no regrets.

