♫I'm afraid the autumn wind will stir up memories♫

166
00:12:42,080 --> 00:12:44,790
♫They unfold, one page after another♫

167
00:12:45,210 --> 00:12:48,670
♫That year, that year♫

168
00:12:49,050 --> 00:12:52,230
♫The flowers flew under the moon, filling the sky♫

169
00:12:52,760 --> 00:12:56,000
♫Falling to the mud, burying the memories♫

170
00:12:57,340 --> 00:12:59,830
♫Layer after layer♫

171
00:13:00,700 --> 00:13:04,170
♫Another year passed♫

172
00:13:08,060 --> 00:13:11,180
♫Another year passed♫

173
00:13:41,490 --> 00:13:43,150
When the Heavenly Bell stops,

174
00:13:43,980 --> 00:13:45,280
a grand ceremony should be held.

175
00:13:54,450 --> 00:13:55,950
I've been waiting

176
00:13:56,390 --> 00:13:58,510
for this couple's bow for 60,000 years.

177
00:14:10,740 --> 00:14:11,980
The Purple Moon?

178
00:14:12,250 --> 00:14:13,870
You have lost all your five Contemplations and divine power.

179
00:14:13,870 --> 00:14:15,010
With such a mortal body,

180
00:14:15,120 --> 00:14:17,390
why can you wield the Purple Lunar Power of Jing Yuan?

181
00:14:17,410 --> 00:14:20,260
Because I have reestablished the divine pact with Fan Yue.

182
00:14:20,390 --> 00:14:22,230
Of course, we can wield what belongs to each other.

183
00:14:26,230 --> 00:14:27,230
Fan Yue,

184
00:14:28,440 --> 00:14:30,280
forgive me for leaving alone.

185
00:14:31,100 --> 00:14:32,720
But before I leave,

186
00:14:33,380 --> 00:14:35,660
I need to borrow something from you.

187
00:14:36,180 --> 00:14:37,730
You will support me,

188
00:14:37,750 --> 00:14:38,520
right?

189
00:15:06,030 --> 00:15:07,300
You should know

190
00:15:07,570 --> 00:15:09,090
you're just a mortal now,

191
00:15:09,110 --> 00:15:10,510
not a deity.

192
00:15:10,540 --> 00:15:12,210
What you've been cultivating all along is Eternal magic.

193
00:15:12,240 --> 00:15:14,180
Now, you've forcibly channeled demonic power into your body.

194
00:15:14,470 --> 00:15:15,360
Even a deity

195
00:15:15,360 --> 00:15:17,250
cannot merge Eternal power with demonic power.

196
00:15:17,270 --> 00:15:18,930
From now on,

197
00:15:19,200 --> 00:15:21,130
you will be tortured by the evil aura every day.

198
00:15:21,750 --> 00:15:23,230
For those ants,

199
00:15:23,250 --> 00:15:24,550
for killing me,

200
00:15:24,980 --> 00:15:26,240
you've turned yourself into a creature

201
00:15:26,270 --> 00:15:28,270
that is neither human, nor Eternal, nor demon.

202
00:15:28,690 --> 00:15:30,210
Is it worth it?

203
00:15:30,490 --> 00:15:32,010
I am not Xing Yue,

204
00:15:32,500 --> 00:15:34,580
nor have I ever thought of becoming a deity.

205
00:15:34,610 --> 00:15:36,000
I am not like her,

206
00:15:36,160 --> 00:15:38,110
born to bring peace to the world.

207
00:15:38,130 --> 00:15:39,580
What I've always wanted

208
00:15:39,700 --> 00:15:40,930
was simply to protect

209
00:15:40,960 --> 00:15:42,040
the people I love and cherish.

210
00:15:42,350 --> 00:15:44,750
But now, the people I love and cherish

211
00:15:44,770 --> 00:15:46,410
have all died or been hurt because of you.

212
00:15:46,440 --> 00:15:47,250
If I don't kill you,

213
00:15:47,270 --> 00:15:50,030
what meaning will my life have,

214
00:15:50,060 --> 00:15:51,380
even if I live on in peace?

215
00:15:51,400 --> 00:15:52,750
I will let you know

216
00:15:53,870 --> 00:15:55,430
that the love and cherishing

217
00:15:56,020 --> 00:15:57,070
you think you have

218
00:15:57,120 --> 00:15:58,510
are all false!

219
00:15:58,510 --> 00:15:59,990
I am the strongest in the world.

220
00:16:00,010 --> 00:16:02,110
Even if I betray the world and kill everyone,

221
00:16:02,140 --> 00:16:04,520
I still love you!

222
00:16:04,720 --> 00:16:06,460
But why?

223
00:16:07,250 --> 00:16:08,760
It has been 60,000 years,

224
00:16:10,260 --> 00:16:13,270
and you've always treated my heart like worthless trash

225
00:16:13,270 --> 00:16:15,150
and never treasured it even for a moment!

226
00:16:15,660 --> 00:16:17,560
Love is not just about receiving.

227
00:16:18,180 --> 00:16:19,890
Love is also about sacrifice.

228
00:16:20,410 --> 00:16:21,300
It's about giving.

229
00:16:21,720 --> 00:16:24,570
But everything you do is murder and possession.

230
00:16:24,670 --> 00:16:27,240
What you do is only to satisfy your own selfish desires.

231
00:16:27,600 --> 00:16:28,600
Mo Li,

232
00:16:29,550 --> 00:16:31,440
you don't have a true heart,

233
00:16:31,960 --> 00:16:33,240
and you don't know love.

234
00:16:33,870 --> 00:16:35,600
If I can drag you and Hidden Heart to death with me,

235
00:16:35,600 --> 00:16:36,790
then today,

236
00:16:37,210 --> 00:16:39,450
even if I die here,

237
00:16:39,470 --> 00:16:40,750
it would be worth it.

238
00:16:54,020 --> 00:16:55,750
I did nothing wrong.

239
00:16:56,260 --> 00:16:58,140
It's the world that is foolish.

240
00:17:16,390 --> 00:17:17,319
Fan Yue?

241
00:17:31,260 --> 00:17:32,890
You fixed the arrow?

242
00:17:33,120 --> 00:17:34,190
Tian Huo did it.

243
00:17:34,730 --> 00:17:36,310
She sacrificed herself to the arrow

244
00:17:36,510 --> 00:17:37,870
and recasted it.

245
00:17:39,550 --> 00:17:41,380
The Xing Yue Divine Bow has long been destroyed.

246
00:17:41,400 --> 00:17:42,880
How did you find it?

247
00:17:43,180 --> 00:17:44,650
The Divine Bow reappeared in the world

248
00:17:44,680 --> 00:17:45,880
because of you.

249
00:17:45,990 --> 00:17:47,740
Fu Ling is the bow spirit of the Divine Bow.

250
00:17:48,340 --> 00:17:49,210
When she died,

251
00:17:49,850 --> 00:17:51,020
the Divine Bow appeared.

252
00:17:54,190 --> 00:17:56,440
No wonder she could hurt me.

253
00:17:56,660 --> 00:17:57,870
Heaven,

254
00:17:57,900 --> 00:17:59,860
you really are cunning.

255
00:18:00,050 --> 00:18:02,410
You actually made the bow spirit of the Divine Bow fall in love with Chong Zhao.

256
00:18:02,670 --> 00:18:04,280
You think that with such a bond,

257
00:18:04,300 --> 00:18:05,850
you can stop me?

258
00:18:07,100 --> 00:18:08,430
Dream on.

259
00:18:09,070 --> 00:18:10,270
You keep saying

260
00:18:10,290 --> 00:18:11,450
that I don't know love

261
00:18:11,480 --> 00:18:12,650
and I deserve to die.

262
00:18:13,120 --> 00:18:15,950
Today, I will let you see with your own eyes

263
00:18:15,970 --> 00:18:18,420
how foolish so-called true love

264
00:18:18,450 --> 00:18:19,920
and sacrifice are?

265
00:18:26,890 --> 00:18:27,700
How could it be?

266
00:18:33,890 --> 00:18:35,110
60,000 years ago,

267
00:18:35,110 --> 00:18:37,740
I fell beneath the Xing Yue Divine Bow.

268
00:18:37,890 --> 00:18:39,310
Do you think that after 60,000 years,

269
00:18:39,310 --> 00:18:40,510
I still don't have a way

270
00:18:40,510 --> 00:18:41,790
to deal with this one and only divine weapon

271
00:18:41,790 --> 00:18:43,510
that could threaten me?

272
00:18:43,700 --> 00:18:45,850
My Hidden power is even stronger than before.

273
00:18:46,070 --> 00:18:47,920
And you are just a mortal.

274
00:18:48,730 --> 00:18:50,770
The mere Xing Yue Divine Bow

275
00:18:51,680 --> 00:18:53,670
can no longer hurt me.

276
00:19:10,610 --> 00:19:11,610
Chong Zhao!

277
00:19:11,640 --> 00:19:12,880
What are you doing?

278
00:19:25,090 --> 00:19:26,340
Chong Zhao,

279
00:19:26,750 --> 00:19:29,290
you actually managed to stop me from entering my sea of consciousness?

280
00:19:29,410 --> 00:19:30,990
Shuo! Fan Yue!

281
00:19:31,450 --> 00:19:32,660
It's Zhao.

282
00:19:32,990 --> 00:19:35,030
Zhao, wake up!

283
00:19:40,710 --> 00:19:42,280
You've always been arrogant and conceited,

284
00:19:42,310 --> 00:19:44,350
which is why you forgot a saying in this world:

285
00:19:44,380 --> 00:19:45,860
"Lie in wait to deceive the enemy,

286
00:19:45,880 --> 00:19:47,530
store up strength to wait for the right moment."

287
00:19:47,560 --> 00:19:49,080
I indeed can't kill you

288
00:19:49,100 --> 00:19:50,650
and can't leave the sea of consciousness.

289
00:19:50,680 --> 00:19:52,130
But if I exhaust my Eternal power,

290
00:19:52,160 --> 00:19:53,550
I can still hold you off for a while.

291
00:19:53,570 --> 00:19:54,650
Chong Zhao!

292
00:19:54,740 --> 00:19:56,280
What are you doing?

293
00:20:00,920 --> 00:20:01,810
Shuo,

294
00:20:01,830 --> 00:20:03,510
I've survived this long

295
00:20:03,540 --> 00:20:05,670
because Xi was still alive at that time.

296
00:20:05,690 --> 00:20:06,690
I once had an unrealistic hope,

297
00:20:06,720 --> 00:20:08,880
wanting to reclaim my body and be with her.

298
00:20:09,150 --> 00:20:11,560
I know my death can only severely wound Mo Li

299
00:20:11,580 --> 00:20:13,070
and can't kill him.

300
00:20:13,270 --> 00:20:15,380
So after Xi died, I've been waiting.

301
00:20:15,110 --> 00:20:19,400
♫No matter if I'm drunk or not, I just want to be reckless once♫

302
00:20:15,880 --> 00:20:18,410
I've been waiting for a chance to give him a fatal blow.

303
00:20:19,120 --> 00:20:20,560
Now, I've got it.

304
00:20:21,650 --> 00:20:26,980
♫Because love is thrilling♫

305
00:20:25,220 --> 00:20:26,910
My death will be worth it.

306
00:20:27,620 --> 00:20:31,120
♫If you tear open my heart♫

307
00:20:27,920 --> 00:20:29,050
Shuo,

308
00:20:29,070 --> 00:20:30,070
Fan Yue,

309
00:20:30,100 --> 00:20:31,990
don't show any mercy.

310
00:20:31,920 --> 00:20:34,230
♫I can hold you a little tighter♫

311
00:20:32,210 --> 00:20:33,030
Remember,

312
00:20:34,190 --> 00:20:35,710
kill Mo Li,

313
00:20:34,780 --> 00:20:39,220
♫This pain will gradually fade♫

314
00:20:36,500 --> 00:20:37,710
and save the world!

315
00:20:41,840 --> 00:20:45,430
♫Time withers the moonlight♫

316
00:20:45,910 --> 00:20:48,390
♫All that's left is pitch darkness♫

317
00:20:48,790 --> 00:20:50,550
♫I want to tear apart♫

318
00:20:51,580 --> 00:20:54,230
♫This sky for you♫

319
00:20:55,160 --> 00:20:57,320
♫A lifetime of guarding everything with you♫

320
00:20:57,940 --> 00:21:01,340
♫Crossing the abyss to fulfill our vow♫

321
00:21:01,500 --> 00:21:02,450
Zhao!

322
00:21:02,060 --> 00:21:05,130
♫I'll leap without a thought for tomorrow♫

323
00:21:05,740 --> 00:21:08,230
♫This moment feels like forever♫

324
00:21:08,450 --> 00:21:11,510
♫I've missed too much time in my life♫

325
00:21:11,910 --> 00:21:15,370
♫I'll throw myself into this flame for you♫

326
00:21:15,920 --> 00:21:17,910
♫Even if I'll perish♫

327
00:21:17,960 --> 00:21:20,510
♫At least I can still kiss your face♫

328
00:21:20,960 --> 00:21:24,220
♫Burn out my waning moon♫

329
00:21:24,980 --> 00:21:32,720
♫In exchange for a lifetime of passion♫

330
00:21:31,510 --> 00:21:32,310
Zhao.

331
00:22:03,770 --> 00:22:04,720
Mo Li,

332
00:22:05,940 --> 00:22:06,980
you've lost.

333
00:22:07,890 --> 00:22:09,730
In the end,

334
00:22:10,100 --> 00:22:12,300
sacrifice defeated your evil.

335
00:22:17,420 --> 00:22:19,040
Do you think

336
00:22:19,440 --> 00:22:22,030
I would die so easily?

337
00:22:33,700 --> 00:22:35,560
Back then, even Xing Yue and Jing Yuan

338
00:22:35,590 --> 00:22:38,430
couldn't destroy my Hidden Heart with the Xing Yue Bow.

339
00:22:38,790 --> 00:22:41,070
Do you think you can do it?

340
00:22:42,020 --> 00:22:44,270
Now, I've grown even stronger.

341
00:22:44,800 --> 00:22:46,480
Chong Zhao is dead,

342
00:22:46,500 --> 00:22:48,720
and this body is about to vanish.

343
00:22:49,120 --> 00:22:51,840
Then I will use the power of the entire world

344
00:22:51,860 --> 00:22:54,100
to rebuild my divine body!

345
00:22:58,330 --> 00:22:59,810
The Hidden Heart?

346
00:23:51,180 --> 00:23:52,050
Fan Yue!

347
00:24:15,000 --> 00:24:16,460
Even if you use yourself as the vessel,

348
00:24:16,920 --> 00:24:18,930
you still can't trap me!

349
00:24:19,980 --> 00:24:21,300
For me,

350
00:24:21,320 --> 00:24:22,560
nothing is impossible.

351
00:24:22,590 --> 00:24:23,690
It's just

352
00:24:23,720 --> 00:24:25,300
a matter of destroying both you and me!

353
00:24:28,320 --> 00:24:29,230
Fan Yue!

354
00:24:30,080 --> 00:24:31,430
What are you doing?

355
00:24:31,710 --> 00:24:32,910
Stop it!

356
00:24:33,300 --> 00:24:34,170
Shuo,

357
00:24:34,600 --> 00:24:35,880
do you still remember

358
00:24:36,170 --> 00:24:38,140
the promise you made to me

359
00:24:38,200 --> 00:24:39,930
on the cliff in the Polar Region?

360
00:24:42,490 --> 00:24:44,750
I'll take care of Bright Moon Palace for you.

361
00:24:46,060 --> 00:24:47,860
I'll accompany Tian Huo.

362
00:24:48,930 --> 00:24:50,690
I'll go and see

363
00:24:52,380 --> 00:24:54,720
every mountain and river on the Eastern Continent,

364
00:24:56,700 --> 00:24:59,280
guarding every star, sun, and moon.

365
00:25:01,450 --> 00:25:02,450
I promise you.

366
00:25:04,700 --> 00:25:05,860
You said

367
00:25:08,940 --> 00:25:10,960
you'd never leave me alone again.

368
00:25:12,210 --> 00:25:13,950
Let the calamity from 60,000 years ago

369
00:25:14,430 --> 00:25:16,230
end today!

370
00:25:16,600 --> 00:25:18,960
Don't leave this pain to future generations!

371
00:25:19,380 --> 00:25:20,610
Fan Yue,

372
00:25:20,740 --> 00:25:23,440
you can't trap me!

373
00:25:28,810 --> 00:25:30,220
Do it, Shuo!

374
00:25:30,250 --> 00:25:32,310
Release the true Xing Yue Arrow.

375
00:25:32,330 --> 00:25:34,600
Let's put an end to all of this together!

376
00:25:36,510 --> 00:25:39,460
You're asking me to send you to your death with my own hands.

377
00:25:40,010 --> 00:25:41,970
I bear the Divine Mantle of the Demon Lord

378
00:25:42,500 --> 00:25:44,410
and the responsibility for all living beings.

379
00:25:44,690 --> 00:25:46,330
I'm willing to die.

380
00:25:46,600 --> 00:25:48,850
It's not for the mission bestowed upon me by the Heaven,

381
00:25:49,690 --> 00:25:51,210
but for you,

382
00:25:51,870 --> 00:25:54,820
and for the countless living beings in this world!

383
00:25:55,040 --> 00:25:56,680
I don't know what a deity should do.

384
00:25:57,520 --> 00:25:58,800
But I know this is what I,

385
00:25:59,600 --> 00:26:02,180
Fan Yue, the Demon King of the Polar Region, must do.

386
00:26:04,610 --> 00:26:11,370
♫If the wind intends to fill the sky with flowers♫

387
00:26:10,360 --> 00:26:11,740
If the Hidden Heart reappears,

388
00:26:12,000 --> 00:26:17,820
♫The moon's brightness is also the result of stars falling into place♫

389
00:26:12,000 --> 00:26:13,340
the Eastern Continent will definitely be destroyed!

390
00:26:13,530 --> 00:26:14,700
You know it.

391
00:26:15,500 --> 00:26:17,070
It's the only way.

392
00:26:17,600 --> 00:26:19,060
Draw your bow, Shuo!

393
00:26:19,330 --> 00:26:22,020
♫As the wind stirs, the clouds gather♫

394
00:26:23,180 --> 00:26:26,530
♫As the clouds shift, the moon becomes full♫

395
00:26:26,830 --> 00:26:33,250
♫Love is the hardest thing to understand♫

396
00:26:34,000 --> 00:26:40,660
♫I'm finally back to where it all started♫

397
00:26:41,420 --> 00:26:47,840
♫All the answers are already explained♫

398
00:26:49,200 --> 00:26:51,490
♫I'll owe you all of my life♫

399
00:26:52,390 --> 00:26:55,610
♫But we're destined to part♫

400
00:26:56,370 --> 00:27:02,430
♫How can I downplay this?♫

401
00:27:02,910 --> 00:27:05,970
♫When you engrave your love into my heart♫

402
00:27:06,670 --> 00:27:09,780
♫When my star falls only for you♫

403
00:27:10,460 --> 00:27:12,000
♫When the heavens fall♫

404
00:27:12,510 --> 00:27:17,340
♫I can still connect with you through the waning moon♫

405
00:27:17,960 --> 00:27:20,640
♫When my pain blurs my eyes♫

406
00:27:19,000 --> 00:27:21,680
I'm willing to exchange my life

407
00:27:21,290 --> 00:27:25,420
♫Out of the countless stars, I see only you♫

408
00:27:23,460 --> 00:27:25,400
for the peace...

409
00:27:25,920 --> 00:27:27,830
of a city!

410
00:27:25,950 --> 00:27:30,540
♫As you turn into a falling star♫

411
00:27:29,960 --> 00:27:31,480
The world is vast.

412
00:27:31,500 --> 00:27:32,500
The journey ahead is long.

413
00:27:33,220 --> 00:27:34,200
Promise me,

414
00:27:34,580 --> 00:27:36,600
No matter what happens in the future,

415
00:27:36,630 --> 00:27:38,220
you must continue

416
00:27:38,580 --> 00:27:40,260
to live freely like now.

417
00:27:41,350 --> 00:27:43,670
I hope Master lives a long life without worries,

418
00:27:43,750 --> 00:27:45,300
that the Bright Moon Palace

419
00:27:45,340 --> 00:27:46,790
is the best in the Demon Race,

420
00:27:46,820 --> 00:27:48,780
that Cang Shan eats a lot every day,

421
00:27:48,810 --> 00:27:51,330
and that Tian Huo lives with me happily.

422
00:27:51,350 --> 00:27:55,350
Life is the process of going from having nothing

423
00:27:55,380 --> 00:27:57,580
to having nothing again.

424
00:27:57,820 --> 00:27:59,930
I've always loved freedom.

425
00:27:59,950 --> 00:28:01,230
Now,

426
00:28:01,700 --> 00:28:04,270
I'm finally free.

427
00:28:04,600 --> 00:28:05,920
I'm like the morning light,

428
00:28:05,940 --> 00:28:07,220
while you are like the stars.

429
00:28:07,250 --> 00:28:08,860
The stars shine brightly

430
00:28:08,880 --> 00:28:10,190
as the moon emerges from the clouds.

431
00:28:11,320 --> 00:28:12,690
You must forever,

432
00:28:14,670 --> 00:28:15,840
always...

433
00:28:16,800 --> 00:28:19,660
be that unbreakable Bai Shuo.

434
00:28:20,510 --> 00:28:21,340
I am just...

435
00:28:22,960 --> 00:28:25,490
going to find them.

436
00:28:25,520 --> 00:28:26,800
In this life,

437
00:28:27,470 --> 00:28:30,560
being able to follow you...

438
00:28:32,410 --> 00:28:34,250
leaves me...

439
00:28:35,930 --> 00:28:37,090
with no regrets.

440
00:28:49,850 --> 00:28:51,460
The sixth Contemplation,

441
00:28:51,730 --> 00:28:53,040
the Contemplation of great love.

442
00:29:03,900 --> 00:29:05,030
It's been 60,000 years,

443
00:29:05,060 --> 00:29:06,040
Shuo.

444
00:29:08,030 --> 00:29:10,160
So many deaths were the price

445
00:29:10,420 --> 00:29:13,140
for this one chance to give him a fatal blow!

446
00:29:13,780 --> 00:29:15,850
Don't waste their sacrifice!

447
00:29:17,770 --> 00:29:18,920
Do it!

448
00:29:46,410 --> 00:29:49,440
♫Across thousands of miles♫

449
00:29:54,410 --> 00:29:59,030
♫The pain of parting lingers♫

450
00:30:02,060 --> 00:30:08,780
♫ I light a lamp with no wick to carry me through the rest of my days♫

451
00:30:10,220 --> 00:30:15,070
♫Flowers in the wind, sand in the water♫

452
00:30:12,240 --> 00:30:13,160
Fan Yue.

453
00:30:18,150 --> 00:30:23,260
♫What kind of tree never takes root?♫

454
00:30:25,910 --> 00:30:31,320
♫What kind of roots never turn into trees?♫

455
00:30:32,940 --> 00:30:34,490
It doesn't hurt.

456
00:30:33,980 --> 00:30:41,290
♫To break the roots of love, to look at the past and seal one's heart♫

457
00:30:35,420 --> 00:30:37,070
How could you

458
00:30:38,960 --> 00:30:41,180
make me make such a decision?

459
00:30:41,940 --> 00:30:46,730
♫I'm your wanderer♫

460
00:30:47,910 --> 00:30:49,600
The Shuo I know

461
00:30:50,170 --> 00:30:54,700
♫The flowers flew away♫

462
00:30:50,230 --> 00:30:52,400
is the bravest person in the world.

463
00:30:52,440 --> 00:30:53,980
In the future,

464
00:30:54,610 --> 00:30:56,910
you'll live well, right?

465
00:30:57,870 --> 00:31:03,590
♫My tears are streaming down like rain♫

466
00:31:06,580 --> 00:31:13,460
♫Light my heart's lamp, cast away attachments, and ask the world♫

467
00:31:14,410 --> 00:31:20,260
♫On the vast sea, you and I♫

468
00:31:24,670 --> 00:31:26,390
Are you leaving?

469
00:31:37,360 --> 00:31:38,430
Shuo,

470
00:31:40,710 --> 00:31:41,860
the wind is rising.

471
00:32:03,790 --> 00:32:07,620
♫The flowers flew away♫

472
00:32:10,390 --> 00:32:11,590
Shuo.

473
00:32:11,150 --> 00:32:16,410
♫My tears are streaming down like rain♫

474
00:32:12,820 --> 00:32:14,100
I will always be with you.

475
00:32:16,040 --> 00:32:17,860
I'll turn into stars,

476
00:32:19,080 --> 00:32:20,510
into the sun and moon,

477
00:32:19,310 --> 00:32:26,000
♫Light my heart's lamp, cast away attachments, and ask the world♫

478
00:32:22,550 --> 00:32:24,870
into every breeze

479
00:32:25,860 --> 00:32:27,670
that passes by your side,

480
00:32:27,000 --> 00:32:33,050
♫On the vast sea, you and I♫

481
00:32:29,180 --> 00:32:31,840
always staying with you.

482
00:32:32,470 --> 00:32:33,790
Shuo.

483
00:32:35,300 --> 00:32:37,270
I love you.

484
00:32:37,900 --> 00:32:39,800
♫May I ask, what do the gods see in the world?♫

485
00:32:40,010 --> 00:32:42,100
♫Sadness from infatuation, anger, and parting♫

486
00:32:42,160 --> 00:32:43,950
♫My love brought tears♫

487
00:32:44,200 --> 00:32:45,920
♫Greed for gathering, for holding, and for completeness♫

488
00:32:46,340 --> 00:32:48,170
♫I was never a flower, but I withered on my own♫

489
00:32:48,380 --> 00:32:49,800
♫I fell between your brows and became a good fruit♫

490
00:32:50,010 --> 00:32:51,690
♫The grand dream of life is hard to let go♫

491
00:32:52,000 --> 00:32:53,980
♫Searching for the path, the answers, yet found nothing♫

492
00:32:54,340 --> 00:32:55,920
♫With a heart full of compassion for the people, I let go of my obsessions♫

493
00:32:56,170 --> 00:32:57,820
♫I cultivated myself to be free of desires, offering myself as a sacrifice to the moon♫

494
00:32:58,090 --> 00:33:00,200
♫The daylight burns through, and the stars shine bright♫

495
00:33:00,510 --> 00:33:02,090
♫Through the Buddhist dust, I see the moon in the sky♫

496
00:33:12,430 --> 00:33:14,080
I used to think

497
00:33:14,100 --> 00:33:15,670
that Jing Lei was impulsive

498
00:33:16,220 --> 00:33:18,460
and always making noise in my ears.

499
00:33:18,750 --> 00:33:20,430
Now that he's gone,

500
00:33:20,460 --> 00:33:22,170
I find it a bit lonely.

501
00:33:22,570 --> 00:33:23,360
I'm not used to it.

502
00:33:26,610 --> 00:33:28,300
I'm still here.

503
00:33:28,330 --> 00:33:29,330
Before, with Jing Lei around,

504
00:33:29,350 --> 00:33:30,940
there was no chance for me to show myself.

505
00:33:30,970 --> 00:33:31,940
As long as you like,

506
00:33:31,960 --> 00:33:32,710
I can

507
00:33:32,740 --> 00:33:34,440
chatter in your ear all day,

508
00:33:34,440 --> 00:33:35,960
making it so noisy that you can't enjoy your food

509
00:33:35,960 --> 00:33:36,880
or sleep at night.

510
00:33:36,880 --> 00:33:38,160
Alright.

511
00:33:38,650 --> 00:33:40,280
You two are now the two Sect Leaders

512
00:33:40,310 --> 00:33:42,680
jointly in charge of Lanling.

513
00:33:42,700 --> 00:33:44,940
It's inappropriate to bicker all day.

514
00:33:45,660 --> 00:33:47,480
No, no.

515
00:33:48,200 --> 00:33:51,400
From now on, there will be no Sect Leader in Lanling.

516
00:33:51,420 --> 00:33:53,560
The three of us will supervise each other

517
00:33:53,590 --> 00:33:55,910
and jointly protect the world.

518
00:33:56,060 --> 00:33:57,370
That's true.

519
00:33:57,390 --> 00:33:58,590
The key responsibility of the Eternals

520
00:33:58,620 --> 00:33:59,790
lies in establishing the right way,

521
00:33:59,810 --> 00:34:01,360
not in seeking power.

522
00:34:01,550 --> 00:34:03,310
The Eternals finally found peace.

523
00:34:04,200 --> 00:34:05,760
It's just a pity

524
00:34:05,820 --> 00:34:07,770
that Chong Zhao will never come back.

525
00:34:09,770 --> 00:34:12,210
Perhaps this is just how things are in the world—

526
00:34:12,230 --> 00:34:13,630
rarely perfect.

527
00:34:15,710 --> 00:34:17,469
In this turmoil of the Hidden Lord,

528
00:34:17,540 --> 00:34:19,420
all the races worked together.

529
00:34:19,449 --> 00:34:22,090
In fact, whether they are Eternals, demons, humans,

530
00:34:22,110 --> 00:34:23,310
or Outlanders,

531
00:34:23,659 --> 00:34:26,179
as long as they have a heart to protect all living beings,

532
00:34:26,210 --> 00:34:27,440
they are our kindred spirits

533
00:34:28,139 --> 00:34:31,540
and should be respected by Lanling.

534
00:34:32,980 --> 00:34:34,380
But if you ask me,

535
00:34:34,409 --> 00:34:36,760
the one who deserves respect the most

536
00:34:36,780 --> 00:34:38,300
is Bai Shuo.

537
00:34:38,330 --> 00:34:39,639
Over the past 60,000 years,

538
00:34:39,670 --> 00:34:40,860
who would have thought that

539
00:34:40,880 --> 00:34:43,020
a mortal could become a deity?

540
00:34:43,469 --> 00:34:44,800
A deity

541
00:34:44,820 --> 00:34:47,050
is not defined by how high one's spiritual power is

542
00:34:47,080 --> 00:34:49,550
or by bloodlines,

543
00:34:49,590 --> 00:34:51,070
but by

544
00:34:51,100 --> 00:34:53,280
having a great heart full of love.

545
00:34:54,280 --> 00:34:56,650
Although Bai Shuo inherited the Divine Mantle of Supreme Deity Xing Yue,

546
00:34:57,090 --> 00:34:59,050
she did not become Supreme Deity Xing Yue.

547
00:34:59,620 --> 00:35:03,000
Instead, with her own strength, she became Supreme Deity Bai Shuo

548
00:35:03,610 --> 00:35:05,250
and forged

549
00:35:05,270 --> 00:35:07,240
her own path.

550
00:35:05,590 --> 00:35:08,050
[Tomb of My Father, Bai Xun]

551
00:35:14,940 --> 00:35:18,860
[Tomb of My Father, Bai Xun]

552
00:35:15,300 --> 00:35:16,410
Father,

553
00:35:17,420 --> 00:35:18,810
I've come to see you.

