642
00:39:28,740 --> 00:39:32,020
the true identity of the guide.

643
00:40:02,200 --> 00:40:03,350
Master Sun?

644
00:40:06,500 --> 00:40:07,770
You are not a mortal.

645
00:40:07,840 --> 00:40:10,400
Even I cannot see through your power.

646
00:40:10,420 --> 00:40:11,650
Who exactly are you?

647
00:40:11,900 --> 00:40:13,110
Who am I?

648
00:40:13,530 --> 00:40:14,930
60,000 years ago,

649
00:40:14,960 --> 00:40:16,440
on the Lunar Hidden Sea,

650
00:40:16,460 --> 00:40:18,460
didn't you ask me the same question?

651
00:40:22,380 --> 00:40:23,370
You are...

652
00:40:23,540 --> 00:40:25,580
I am neither a being of this world

653
00:40:25,600 --> 00:40:27,750
