678
00:41:29,600 --> 00:41:33,000
the only exception in the world over the past ten thousand years.

679
00:41:33,020 --> 00:41:35,090
You also proved to me

680
00:41:35,120 --> 00:41:36,430
that Heaven

681
00:41:36,450 --> 00:41:37,660
