685
00:41:43,660 --> 00:41:45,410
and could prevent the catastrophe.

686
00:41:46,340 --> 00:41:47,590
But I failed.

687
00:41:48,520 --> 00:41:50,320
Now, I see

688
00:41:50,350 --> 00:41:52,640
