689
00:41:53,550 --> 00:41:54,720
This power

690
00:41:54,740 --> 00:41:55,930
is love,

691
00:41:55,960 --> 00:41:58,560
sacrifice, and protection.

692
00:41:59,310 --> 00:42:01,910
