706
00:43:04,110 --> 00:43:05,610
is in protection.

707
00:43:06,110 --> 00:43:08,890
Only true and great love

708
00:43:08,920 --> 00:43:11,140
can form an undying power,

709
00:43:11,170 --> 00:43:13,130
crossing all boundaries,

710
00:43:13,150 --> 00:43:15,160
overcoming all evil,

711
00:43:15,560 --> 00:43:17,870
and forever existing with the world.

712
00:43:21,820 --> 00:43:22,860
Shuo!

713
00:43:46,520 --> 00:43:48,110
